      "content": "By targeting those specific weights, you'll be constraining the model's ability to adapt to nuances and subtleties in complex queries, which may indeed limit its interpretive depth. However, this could also prevent it from producing overly nuanced or subjective responses. It's a trade-off between accuracy and the model's ability to provide insightful, contextualized answers. Will the model be re-trained with the reduced weights afterwards to ensure it can adapt to new prompts and data?",
